Hash[ary]
^^^^^^^^^ Style/HashConversion: Prefer `ary.to_h` to `Hash[ary]`.
Hash[a, b, c, d]
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Style/HashConversion: Prefer literal hash to `Hash[arg1, arg2, ...]`.
