^^^^^^ Style/HashConversion: Prefer literal hash to `Hash[arg1, arg2, ...]`.
Hash[a: b, c: d]
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Style/HashConversion: Prefer literal hash to `Hash[key: value, ...]`.
